        "id": "WeakenAllAMusashiRegularBoss",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Sword Virtuoso",
          "description": "Weakens all enemies. The user is granted a Sleep Ward, Stun Ward, Poison Ward, will Endure the next damage that would defeat it with 1HP, and gains the Armor status effect. Armor grants 50% damage reduction from the next attack, then the effect is removed.\n\nEach Ward prevents their named effect from being applied once, then is removed. Identical Wards and Endure effects cannot stack. This skill becomes locked for 20TU after use. Usable if this unit has not defeated any units with attacks or Absolute Zero while on the battlefield.\n\nWeakened units have their Attack reduced to 0.75x until the end of their next turn. This effect will overwrite any existing Weak or Enrage effects on affected units. The effect of Weakening may be diminished if the affected unit's Attack is increased by other effects and it can be overwritten by Enrage effects.",
          "selected": "Gains Wards, Endure & Armor"
